		<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="400" y="+6" x="12" type="text">		<![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">In your report you are expected to describe all the important information shown in the chart or graph and to comment on the most significant trends. You are not expected, and you will not have time, to describe every detail. This means that before you write, you must decide which information should be included and which information does not need to be mentioned.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
