		<paragraph x="0" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">D. This is neither the biggest difference between radio and newspapers that existed during the period, nor the smallest.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
