	<feedback mode="101" id="5">
		<paragraph x="0" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">E. The report should compare figures for the three media at the same point in time. Comparing radio in one year with newspapers in another doesn't tell us very much about their relative popularity.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
